Files and Windows
=================

,f to start the fuzzy finder
Use Ctrl+V to open the file in a new vertical split.
Use Ctrl+C to close the fuzzy finder.

:vnew to create a new vertical split
Ctrl+W h to move Left
Ctrl+W l to move Right
Ctrl+W r to rotate the window order

Surround
========
cs starts a surround replacement, example "Test" becomes 'Test' with cs"'

